<title>USA: TABLE - Hyperion Software Q4 net rises.</title>
<headline>TABLE - Hyperion Software Q4 net rises.</headline>
<dateline>STAMFORD, Conn. 1997-07-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>(In thousands, except per share data)</p>
<p>				    Quarter Ended	 Year Ended</p>
<p>					June 30,	     June 30,</p>
<p>				    1997	1996	1997     1996</p>
<p>Statement of Income Data:</p>
<p>Software license revenues</p>
<p>				  $41,799   $35,110 $112,115 $ 90,304</p>
